To read the TomeNET-Guide double-click it in your TomeNET folder, or read it at
http://www.tomenet.eu/ or simply press '\{B?\{w' again here to view it in-game!

Don't get discouraged! If you are new to TomeNET, you will die..... a lot.
But, as you get more experienced you will become better at surviving. Have fun!

1. chat with ':' (colon) key, say hi after logging on. :D
2. the training tower is a good place to start. It's entrance symbol is '\{g<\{w'.
   Press SHIFT+m to see a map of town to see where it is located.
3. press CTRL+q to quit and auto-save window layout. Do it in town to be safe!
